She smiled at Prebon, "Should I be getting ready for your little talk 
with Ramulus? Or shall I stay with you?" as she nuzzled against him.
"Just make sure that they have a tighter grip on Striker than they 
have on me. I won't be going anywhere without you.  My master."  She 
kissed his cheek and held him close.
